has positive curvature—

00:11:32.630 --> 00:11:35.630
making it a hyposphere—and the curvature

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:39.080
is the maximum that it could be,
given the current flatness measurements.

00:11:39.260 --> 00:11:40.860
But if you travelled that distance—

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:44.580
again, assuming the universe froze in its expansion, which it won't—

00:11:44.580 --> 00:11:48.320
then you'd get back to your starting point
a long, long, long time later.

00:11:48.510 --> 00:11:50.520
If you travelled at
the speed of light,

00:11:50.525 --> 00:11:54.310
it would take around
750 billion years,

00:11:54.310 --> 00:11:57.980
